snippet.title: North American Hunting Extravaganza
snippet.description:
http://www.ebgames.com.au/wii-153071-North-American-Hunting-Extravaganza-Nintendo-Wii

Head out into the wild to track and hunt the most dangerous game in North America. Become a master hunter by travelling across the country and honing your skills to go after bigger and more dangerous prey. Set your sights on over 20 different wildlife species, with a variety weapons and hunting equipment at your disposal.
